description:
This photo was taken in New York in December 2018 during my Christmas stay in the city. I was wandering the streets and was amazed by a pile of coffee-to-go cups and decided to take a picture. 

I would call this photo "Trash-To-Go" because the cups are used only a few minutes till they are trash.

This photo is my most downloaded photo. I see this photo is constantly used to raise awareness of single-use plastic. Keep up the good work!
